 ðŸ”¹ Key Differences 

| Feature          | NACL             | Security Group / NSG        |
| ---------------- | ---------------- | --------------------------- |
| Level            | Subnet           | VM / NIC                    |
| Stateful         | âŒ No            | âœ… Yes                     |
| Rules            | Allow + Deny     |  Allow only                 |
| Inbound/Outbound | Separate rules   | Return traffic auto-allowed |
| Default behavior | Cloud dependent  | Deny all (implicit)         |




 ðŸ”¹ Linux Admin Role 

