 ðŸ”¹ One-Line Interview  *********imp 

> A Network ACL is a stateless, subnet-level firewall that provides an additional security layer by controlling inbound and outbound traffic for an entire subnet.




NACL = Subnet gate (stateless)
SG = VM gate (stateful)




